<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٠٤٦ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(حب حم)</span> : <span class="c1">" مَنْ قَتَلَهُ بَطْنُهُ لَمْ يُعَذَّبْ فِي قَبْرِهِ "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">فِي مُسْنَدِ:</span> خَالِدِ بْنِ عُرْفُطَةَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>